. 
<emphasis box="[1121,1211,1519,1544]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="41">caribea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Pulitzer­ 
<bibRefCitation author="Finali" box="[264,407,1559,1585]" pageId="2" pageNumber="41" refString="Pulitzer-Finali, G. (1986) A collection of West Indian Demospongiae (Porifera) with, in appendix, a list of the Demospongiae hitherto recorded from the West Indies. Annali del Museo Civico di Storia Naturale di Genova, 86, 65 - 216." type="journal article" year="1986">
Finali, 
<number box="[348,407,1559,1585]" pageId="2" pageNumber="41" value="1986.0">1986</number>
