<taxonomicName box="[697,787,1719,1744]" class="Demospongiae" family="Desmacellidae" genus="Biemna" kingdom="Animalia" order="Poecilosclerida" pageId="2" pageNumber="41" phylum="Porifera" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[697,787,1719,1744]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="41">Biemna</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species have styles as megascleres.
</paragraph>
